PaXy&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=136&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=30  | publisher=華僑日報 |date=1980-10-29 |access-date=2020-02-19 |quote= }}</ref>
