'''呂有慧'''（{{lang-en |Lisa Lui Yau Wai}}，{{bd|1956年|2月12日}}），香港女演員，畢業於1972年第一期[[無綫電視藝員訓練班|無綫電視藝員訓練班]]。其後分別服務過[[麗的電視|麗的電視]]、[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]以及[[香港電視網絡|香港電視]]。現時較少於幕前演出。

==背景==
呂有慧於[[香港|香港]]出生，早年在[[香港島|香港島]][[華富邨|華富邨]]成長。在九兄弟姊妹中排行最細<ref>[http://www.kfzimg.com/sw/kfzimg/2935/0279e708661763de93_b.jpg 玉郎之星呂有慧] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kfzimg.com/sw/kfzimg/2935/0279e708661763de93_b.jpg |date=20210112150808 }} 玉郎電視週刊. 1985年第383期</ref>，其較她年長一歲的胞姊呂有佳曾在1970年代到[[佳藝電視|佳藝電視]]試鏡當演員<ref>{{cite news |title=呂有慧姊妹擬演紅樓夢 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgPMQJTdLU3q5&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1977-08-06 |access-date=2020-02-17 |quote= }}</ref>。父親則為一名古董店老闆<ref name="呂有慧成了女老闆 開古玩店不計餂贃">{{cite news | title=呂有慧成了女老闆 開古玩店不計餂贃 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFLCZwvSdExM7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=119&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=4  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1982-07-11| accessdate=2020-02-19|quote= }}</ref>。呂有慧中學畢業後在1972年參加第一期[[無綫電視藝員訓練班|無綫電視藝員訓練班]]入行，同期有[[陳嘉儀|陳嘉儀]]、[[莊文清|莊文清]]、[[高妙思|高妙思]]、[[蘇杏璇|蘇杏璇]]、[[甘國亮|甘國亮]]等。初期與無綫小生[[伍衛國|伍衛國]]在電視劇經常合演情侶，故有無綫第一代螢幕情侶之稱，代表作是1975年的《[[巫山盟|巫山盟]]》。由於其清秀的臉孔及高挑的身材，使她能夠擔任的角色宜古宜今，尤其在古裝劇中她往往扮演貴婦人（如84版《[[鹿鼎記_(1984年電視劇)|鹿鼎記]]》中的[[皇太后|皇太后]]），或是風塵女子（如《[[武林世家|武林世家]]》中的倪雪）、殺人不眨眼的女魔頭（如83版《[[神鵰俠侶_(1983年電視劇)|神鵰俠侶]]》的[[李莫愁|李莫愁]]）等角色。時裝劇方面，她比較常扮演成熟、精明能幹又堅強的現代女性，很少扮演弱質女子的角色。她於1997年再度加盟[[亞視|亞視]]。

呂有慧於1976年隨[[鍾景輝|鍾景輝]]跳槽麗的電視<ref>{{cite news | title=盛筵不重來 一日難再晨 呂有慧樂天知命 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFCtR7QZe7ZRX&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=15&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=6  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1979-05-17| accessdate=2020-02-17|quote= }}</ref>。她在麗的電視演的第一部劇集叫「愛情故事」，該劇為每集一個獨立故事，呂有慧演出其中一集。該劇播出後，無綫指呂有慧在當時與無綫的合約未完成的情況下，接拍麗的電視的電視劇集，因此要控告麗的和呂有慧<ref>{{cite news | title=與無線尙有生約被禁亮相 呂有慧突接律師信 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFIMfQ6NCX6m3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=100&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=7  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1976-12-07| accessdate=2020-02-19|quote= }}</ref>。最後幾經交涉，大家以息事寧人告終。而呂與當時的丈夫駱貴虎（即演員金童）在1978年入稟法庭就二人各自的私生活報導不實一事控告新時代出版公司<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧與夫控訴秘聞雜誌誹謗 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFPWtsuFmZTU5&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=1  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1978-01-31| accessdate=2020-02-17|quote= }}</ref>。最終獲得十五萬賠償<ref>{{cite news | title=控「秘聞」雜誌誹謗 金童呂有慧得直 官判賠償十五萬 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgNusb8uVuZEI&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=10&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=8  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1987-09-01| accessdate=2020-02-17|quote= }}</ref>。她在同年11月完成與麗的電視的合約後重投無綫電視<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧回娘家 秘密簽約無綫 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgF0Z85PT4eOM&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=4&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=11  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1978-06-24| accessdate=2020-02-17|quote= }}</ref>，至1997年離開。呂重回無綫往後不再常於電視劇中擔任女主角。她在1982年至1983年仍是電視台藝員時以經營古玩店為副業，不久因經濟不景氣而結束生意<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧很熱衷於做生意 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFDwOW%2BydT%2Fje&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=115&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=4  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1984-03-25| accessdate=2020-02-19|quote= }}</ref><ref name="呂有慧成了女老闆 開古玩店不計餂贃" />。此前在1981年於[[中環|中環]]開設精品店<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧結婚七年 怕金童七年之癢 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv595P2B4OmBy56xGqS2uxt4R&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=163&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=26  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1981-12-22 | accessdate=2020-02-20|quote= }}</ref>。及後於1987年至1989年間移民[[美國|美國]]生活（其時一對子女皆於美國升學）<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧簽無綫兩年 加薪兼有極大自由 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJIrUN0C8gB6r&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=200&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=23  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1989-11-22 | accessdate=2020-02-20|quote= }}</ref>，並在[[三藩市|三藩市]]經營錄影帶公司生意<ref name="呂有慧重視農曆年 男友是生意合夥人 中東戰爭影響美國生意" />。同期也經營古董錶和飾物生意<ref>{{cite news | title=對與金童婚變事 呂有慧拒予證實 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJFnPexSOP1SK&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=198&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=27  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1989-02-09| accessdate=2020-02-20|quote= }}</ref>。

在1990年代，呂有慧返回香港發展。當她在1997年完約後轉投[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]。隨後於2009年再次簽約[[無綫電視|無綫電視]]，接拍電視劇《[[摘星之旅|摘星之旅]]》。直至2011年離開[[無綫電視|無綫電視]]，且於2012年簽約[[香港電視網絡|香港電視]]，成爲旗下藝員<ref>{{cite news | title=元華嘆唔受尊重 轉投王維基 | url=http://archive.ph/Hjiio | format= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2012-02-23| accessdate=2020-02-20|quote= }}</ref>。

==家庭生活==
呂有慧已婚及曾被傳已離婚 32 年<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧激罕與老公金童出席聚會　曾傳離婚傳足32年力破傳聞 | url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/688424/%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%E6%BF%80%E7%BD%95%E8%88%87%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E9%87%91%E7%AB%A5%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83-%E6%9B%BE%E5%82%B3%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A%E5%82%B3%E8%B6%B332%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%A0%B4%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E | publisher=香港 01 | date=2021-10-14 | accessdate=2021-11-17 | quote= | archive-date=2021-11-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117073111/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/688424/%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%E6%BF%80%E7%BD%95%E8%88%87%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E9%87%91%E7%AB%A5%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83-%E6%9B%BE%E5%82%B3%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A%E5%82%B3%E8%B6%B332%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%A0%B4%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E }}</ref>。丈夫是武打演員兼電視台武術指導金童。二人結緣於電影公司在1972年籌備電影《二龍爭珠》（1974年上映）選角過程時，由呂的訓練班同學[[關聰|關聰]]介紹她去當主角，從而認識了金童<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧金童傳婚訊 不想鋪張將往旅行 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59%2F9WIUSQ5l70dyolCC5g5q&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=122&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=33  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1975-02-23| accessdate=2020-02-19|quote= }}</ref>。呂與金後於1975年1月16日結婚<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧談夫婦之道 重容忍為子女幸福著想 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59%2F7w9HmQIJTUk3c9Dao9ci&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=164&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=15  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1986-01-10| accessdate=2020-02-20|quote= }}</ref>。而他們婚後共育有一子一女<ref>{{cite news | title=呂有慧再做媽咪 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2Bn4efK8nHqL0xAovYkFn3P&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=43&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%91%82%E6%9C%89%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1980-10-29 | accessdate=2020-02-18|quote= }}</ref>。

